sequenceDiagram
    participant Architect
    participant CLI
    participant GitManager
    participant Git as Simple-Git
    participant Remote as GitHub

    Architect->>CLI: foundryspec sync
    CLI->>GitManager: new GitManager()
    CLI->>GitManager: sync()
    
    GitManager->>GitManager: Read config (external specs)
    
    loop For each Remote Spec
        GitManager->>FS: Check if target exists
        alt Target Exists
            GitManager->>Git: pull()
            Git->>Remote: Fetch changes
        else Target Missing
            GitManager->>Git: clone()
            Git->>Remote: Clone repo
        end
    end
    
    GitManager-->>CLI: Sync Success
    CLI-->>Architect: âœ… External specs synchronized.
